{"content": "I need to multiply 471 \u00d7 340 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 471\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 324 + 63 + 1 = 388\u2081\u2080\n- 340\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 0 = 279\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 388 \u00d7 279 = 108,252\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 108252 \u00f7 9 = 12028 r 0\n- 12028 \u00f7 9 = 1336 r 4\n- 1336 \u00f7 9 = 148 r 4\n- 148 \u00f7 9 = 16 r 4\n- 16 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 7\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **174440\u2089**\n\n174440", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}